author: AP
title: Tokyo Olympic staffer tests positive for coronavirus
description: A staff member of the Tokyo Olympic organizing committee has tested positive for COVID-19
content:
TOKYO (AP) — A staff member of the Tokyo Olympic organizing committee has tested positive for COVID-19.
